### EU European Council / Council of the European Union Loc ### Other EU scripted Loc see EU_scripted_localisation.txt
###############################################################
defined_text = {
	name = xxx_Loc
	text = {
		trigger = {

		}
		localization_key = xxx_1
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {

		}
		localization_key = xxx_1
	}
}


################################
### 1.1.8.1 voting focus loc ###
################################

#############
### EU001 ###
#############

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU001
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU001
					has_country_flag = focus_EU001_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU001_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU001_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU001
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU001
					has_country_flag = focus_EU001_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU001_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU001
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU001
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU001
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU001_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU001_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU001_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU001_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU001_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU001
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU001_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU001_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU001_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU001_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU001_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU001_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU001_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU001_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU001_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

### Voting TAGs loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU001
	text = {
		trigger = {
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					OR = {
						has_country_flag = focus_EU001_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU001_QMV_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU001_maj_yes
					}
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU001_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_Undecided_TAG_EU001
	text = {
		trigger = {
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					OR = {
						has_country_flag = focus_EU001_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU001_QMV_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU001_maj_yes
					}
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_Undecided_TAG_EU001_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_NO_TAG_EU001
	text = {
		trigger = {
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					OR = {
						has_country_flag = focus_EU001_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU001_QMV_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU001_maj_yes
					}
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_NO_TAG_EU001_loc_key
	}
}

### TAGs EU001 ###


### ALB EU001 ###
defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_ALB_EU001
	text = {
		trigger = {
			ALB = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU001_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_ALB_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_Undecided_ALB_EU001
	text = {
		trigger = {
			ALB = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU001_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = less_than
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU001_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = greater_than
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_ALB_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_NO_ALB_EU001
	text = {
		trigger = {
			ALB = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU001_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = less_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_ALB_loc_key
	}
}

#############
### EU002 ###
#############

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU002
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU002
					has_country_flag = focus_EU002_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU002_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU002_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU002
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU002
					has_country_flag = focus_EU002_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU002_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU002
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU002
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU002
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU002_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU002_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU002_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU002_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU002_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU002
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU002_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU002_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU002_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU002_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU002_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU002_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU002_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU002_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU002_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}

### Voting TAGs loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU002
	text = {
		trigger = {
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					OR = {
						has_country_flag = focus_EU002_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU002_QMV_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU002_maj_yes
					}
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU002_loc_key
	}
}

### ALB EU002 ###
defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_ALB_EU002
	text = {
		trigger = {
			ALB = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU002_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_ALB_loc_key
	}
}

### EU100 ###

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU100
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU100
					has_country_flag = focus_EU100_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU100_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU100_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU100
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU100
					has_country_flag = focus_EU100_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU100_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU100
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU100
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU100
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU100_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU100_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU100_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU100_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU100_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU100
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU100_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU100_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU100_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU100_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU100_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU100_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU100_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU100_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU100_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

		}

	}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_EST_EU100
	text = {
		trigger = {
			EST = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = EST.EU_AI_focus_EU100_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EST_loc_key
	}
}

				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_SLV_loc_key
	}
}

### EU101 ###

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU101
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU101
					has_country_flag = focus_EU101_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU101_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU101_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU101
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU101
					has_country_flag = focus_EU101_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU101_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU101
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU101
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU101
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU101_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU101_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU101_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU101_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU101_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU101
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU101_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU101_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU101_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU101_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU101_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU101_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU101_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU101_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU101_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

			FRA = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = FRA.EU_AI_focus_EU101_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = less_than
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = FRA.EU_AI_focus_EU101_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = greater_than
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_FRA_loc_key
	}
}

			}
			check_variable = {
				var = SWE.EU_AI_focus_EU101_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = greater_than
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_SWE_loc_key
	}
}

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU102
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU102
					has_country_flag = focus_EU102_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU102_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU102_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU102
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU102
					has_country_flag = focus_EU102_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU102_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU102
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU102
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU102
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU102_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU102_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU102_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU102_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU102_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU102
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU102_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU102_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU102_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU102_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU102_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU102_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU102_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU102_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU102_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

	text = {
		trigger = {
			BOS = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = BOS.EU_AI_focus_EU102_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_BOS_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_Undecided_BOS_EU102
	text = {
		trigger = {
			BOS = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = BOS.EU_AI_focus_EU102_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = less_than
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = BOS.EU_AI_focus_EU102_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = greater_than
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_BOS_loc_key
	}
}

				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = TUR.EU_AI_focus_EU102_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = less_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_TUR_loc_key
	}
}

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU103
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU103
					has_country_flag = focus_EU103_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU103_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU103_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU103
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU103
					has_country_flag = focus_EU103_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU103_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU103
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU103
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU103
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU103_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU103_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU103_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU103_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU103_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU103
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU103_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU103_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU103_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU103_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU103_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU103_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU103_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU103_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU103_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

#############
### EU104 ###
#############

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU104
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU104
					has_country_flag = focus_EU104_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU104_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU104_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU104
	text = {
		trigger = {

				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU104
					has_country_flag = focus_EU104_QMV

### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU104
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU104
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU104_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU104_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU104_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU104_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU104_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU104
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU104_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU104_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU104_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU104_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU104_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU104_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU104_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU104_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU104_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

### TAGs EU104 ###


### ALB EU104 ###
defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_ALB_EU104
	text = {
		trigger = {
			ALB = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU104_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_ALB_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_Undecided_ALB_EU104
	text = {
		trigger = {
			ALB = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU104_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = less_than
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU104_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = greater_than
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_ALB_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_NO_ALB_EU104

#############
### EU105 ###
#############

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU105
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU105
					has_country_flag = focus_EU105_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU105_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU105_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU105
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU105
					has_country_flag = focus_EU105_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU105_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU105
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU105
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU105
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU105_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU105_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU105_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU105_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU105_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU105
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU105_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU105_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU105_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU105_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU105_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU105_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU105_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU105_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU105_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

### Voting TAGs loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU105
	text = {
		trigger = {
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					OR = {
						has_country_flag = focus_EU105_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU105_QMV_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU105_maj_yes
					}
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU105_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_Undecided_TAG_EU105
	text = {
		trigger = {
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					OR = {
						has_country_flag = focus_EU105_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU105_QMV_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU105_maj_yes
					}
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_Undecided_TAG_EU105_loc_key
	}
}

			}

				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_SER_loc_key
	}

### EU200 ###

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU200
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU200
					has_country_flag = focus_EU200_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU200_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU200_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU200
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU200
					has_country_flag = focus_EU200_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU200_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU200
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU200
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU200
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU200_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU200_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU200_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU200_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU200_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU200
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU200_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU200_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU200_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU200_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU200_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU200_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU200_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU200_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU200_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

		}

	}

			}
			check_variable = {
				var = SLV.EU_AI_focus_EU200_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = less_than
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = SLV.EU_AI_focus_EU200_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = greater_than
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_SLV_loc_key
	}
}

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU201
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU201
					has_country_flag = focus_EU201_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU201_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU201_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU201
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU201
					has_country_flag = focus_EU201_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU201_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU201
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU201
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU201
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU201_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU201_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU201_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU201_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU201_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU201
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU201_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU201_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU201_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU201_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU201_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU201_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU201_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU201_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU201_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

			SWE = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = SWE.EU_AI_focus_EU201_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = less_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_SWE_loc_key
	}
}

### EU202 ###

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU202
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU202
					has_country_flag = focus_EU202_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU202_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU202_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU202
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU202
					has_country_flag = focus_EU202_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU202_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU202
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU202
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU202
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU202_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU202_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU202_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU202_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU202_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU202
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU202_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU202_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU202_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU202_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU202_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU202_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU202_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU202_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU202_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

		trigger = {
			UKR = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = UKR.EU_AI_focus_EU202_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_UKR_loc_key
	}
}

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU203
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU203
					has_country_flag = focus_EU203_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU203_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU203_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU203
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU203
					has_country_flag = focus_EU203_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU203_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU203
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU203
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU203
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU203_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU203_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU203_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU203_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU203_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU203
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU203_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU203_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU203_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU203_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU203_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU203_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU203_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU203_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU203_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

#############
### EU204 ###
#############

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU204
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU204
					has_country_flag = focus_EU204_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU204_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU204_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU204
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU204
					has_country_flag = focus_EU204_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU204_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU204
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU204
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU204
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU204_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU204_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU204_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU204_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU204_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU204
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU204_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU204_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU204_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU204_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU204_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU204_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU204_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU204_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU204_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

### Voting TAGs loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU204
	text = {
		trigger = {
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					OR = {
						has_country_flag = focus_EU204_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU204_QMV_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU204_maj_yes
					}
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU204_loc_key
	}
}

### TAGs EU204 ###


### ALB EU204 ###
defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_ALB_EU204
	text = {
		trigger = {
			ALB = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU204_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_ALB_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_Undecided_ALB_EU204
	text = {
		trigger = {
			ALB = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU204_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = less_than
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU204_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = greater_than
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_ALB_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_NO_ALB_EU204
	text = {
		trigger = {
			ALB = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}

				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}

			check_variable = {
				var = SCL.EU_AI_focus_EU204_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_SCL_loc_key
	}

#############
### EU205 ###
#############

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU205
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU205
					has_country_flag = focus_EU205_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU205_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU205_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU205
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU205
					has_country_flag = focus_EU205_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU205_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU205
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU205
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU205
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU205_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU205_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU205_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU205_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU205_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU205
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU205_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU205_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU205_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU205_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU205_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU205_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU205_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU205_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU205_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

### Voting TAGs loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU205
	text = {
		trigger = {
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					OR = {
						has_country_flag = focus_EU205_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU205_QMV_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU205_maj_yes
					}
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU205_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_Undecided_TAG_EU205
	text = {
		trigger = {
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					OR = {
						has_country_flag = focus_EU205_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU205_QMV_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU205_maj_yes
					}
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_Undecided_TAG_EU205_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_NO_TAG_EU205
	text = {
		trigger = {
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					OR = {
						has_country_flag = focus_EU205_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU205_QMV_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU205_maj_yes
					}
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_NO_TAG_EU205_loc_key
	}
}

	text = {
		trigger = {
			SER = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = SER.EU_AI_focus_EU205_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = less_than
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = SER.EU_AI_focus_EU205_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = greater_than
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_SER_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_NO_SER_EU205
	text = {
		trigger = {
			SER = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = SER.EU_AI_focus_EU205_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = less_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_SER_loc_key
	}
}

#############
### EU206 ###
#############

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU206
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU206
					has_country_flag = focus_EU206_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU206_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU206_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU206
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU206
					has_country_flag = focus_EU206_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU206_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU206
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU206
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU206
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU206_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU206_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU206_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU206_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU206_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU206
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU206_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU206_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU206_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU206_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU206_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU206_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU206_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU206_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU206_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

### Voting TAGs loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU206
	text = {
		trigger = {
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					OR = {
						has_country_flag = focus_EU206_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU206_QMV_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU206_maj_yes
					}
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU206_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_Undecided_TAG_EU206
	text = {
		trigger = {
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					OR = {
						has_country_flag = focus_EU206_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU206_QMV_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU206_maj_yes
					}
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_Undecided_TAG_EU206_loc_key
	}
}

					}
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_NO_TAG_EU206_loc_key
	}
}

### ALB EU206 ###
defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_ALB_EU206
	text = {
		trigger = {
			ALB = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU206_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_ALB_loc_key
	}
}

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU207
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU207
					has_country_flag = focus_EU207_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU207_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU207_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU207
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU207
					has_country_flag = focus_EU207_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU207_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU207
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU207
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU207
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU207_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU207_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU207_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU207_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU207_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU207
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU207_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU207_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU207_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU207_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU207_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU207_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU207_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU207_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU207_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU208
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU208
					has_country_flag = focus_EU208_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU208_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU208_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU208
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU208
					has_country_flag = focus_EU208_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU208_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU208
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU208
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU208
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU208_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU208_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU208_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU208_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU208_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU208
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU208_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU208_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU208_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU208_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU208_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU208_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU208_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU208_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU208_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU300
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU300
					has_country_flag = focus_EU300_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU300_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU300_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU300
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU300
					has_country_flag = focus_EU300_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU300_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU300
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU300
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU300
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU300_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU300_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU300_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU300_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU300_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU300
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU300_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU300_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU300_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU300_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU300_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU300_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU300_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU300_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU300_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

		trigger = {
			POR = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = POR.EU_AI_focus_EU300_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_POR_loc_key
	}
}

#############
### EU301 ###
#############

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU301
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU301
					has_country_flag = focus_EU301_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU301_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU301_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU301
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU301
					has_country_flag = focus_EU301_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU301_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU301
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU301
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU301
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU301_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU301_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU301_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU301_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU301_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU301
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU301_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU301_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU301_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU301_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU301_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU301_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU301_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU301_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU301_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

### Voting TAGs loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU301
	text = {
		trigger = {
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					OR = {
						has_country_flag = focus_EU301_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU301_QMV_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU301_maj_yes
					}
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU301_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_Undecided_TAG_EU301
	text = {
		trigger = {
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {

					OR = {
						has_country_flag = focus_EU301_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU301_QMV_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU301_maj_yes
					}
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_Undecided_TAG_EU301_loc_key
	}

### TAGs EU301 ###


### ALB EU301 ###
defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_ALB_EU301
	text = {
		trigger = {
			ALB = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU301_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_ALB_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_Undecided_ALB_EU301
	text = {
		trigger = {
			ALB = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU301_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = less_than
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU301_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = greater_than
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_ALB_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_NO_ALB_EU301
	text = {
		trigger = {

				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = SCL.EU_AI_focus_EU301_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = less_than
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = SCL.EU_AI_focus_EU301_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = greater_than
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_SCL_loc_key
	}
}

#############
### EU302 ###
#############

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU302
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU302
					has_country_flag = focus_EU302_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU302_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU302_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU302
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU302
					has_country_flag = focus_EU302_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU302_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU302
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU302
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU302
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU302_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU302_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU302_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU302_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU302_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU302
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU302_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU302_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU302_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU302_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU302_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU302_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU302_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU302_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU302_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

### Voting TAGs loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU302
	text = {
		trigger = {
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					OR = {
						has_country_flag = focus_EU302_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU302_QMV_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU302_maj_yes
					}
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU302_loc_key
	}
}

	name = EU_council_Undecided_TAG_EU302

					OR = {
						has_country_flag = focus_EU302_yes

						has_country_flag = focus_EU302_maj_yes
					}
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_Undecided_TAG_EU302_loc_key
	}

	name = EU_council_NO_TAG_EU302
	text = {
		trigger = {
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					OR = {
						has_country_flag = focus_EU302_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU302_QMV_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU302_maj_yes
					}
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_NO_TAG_EU302_loc_key
	}
}

	name = EU_council_YES_ALB_EU302

		trigger = {
			ALB = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {

				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}

### EU303 ###

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU303
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU303
					has_country_flag = focus_EU303_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU303_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU303_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU303
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU303
					has_country_flag = focus_EU303_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU303_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU303
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU303
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU303
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU303_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU303_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU303_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU303_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU303_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU303
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU303_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU303_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU303_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU303_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU303_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU303_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU303_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU303_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU303_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU304
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU304
					has_country_flag = focus_EU304_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU304_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU304_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU304
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU304
					has_country_flag = focus_EU304_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU304_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU304
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU304
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU304
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU304_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU304_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU304_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU304_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU304_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU304
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU304_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU304_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU304_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU304_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU304_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU304_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU304_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU304_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU304_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

				}

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU305
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU305
					has_country_flag = focus_EU305_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU305_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU305_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU305
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU305
					has_country_flag = focus_EU305_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU305_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU305
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU305
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU305
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU305_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU305_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU305_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU305_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU305_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU305
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU305_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU305_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU305_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU305_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU305_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU305_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU305_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU305_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU305_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

	name = EU_council_YES_NOR_EU305
	text = {
		trigger = {
			NOR = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = NOR.EU_AI_focus_EU305_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_NOR_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_Undecided_NOR_EU305
	text = {
		trigger = {
			NOR = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = NOR.EU_AI_focus_EU305_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = less_than
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = NOR.EU_AI_focus_EU305_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = greater_than
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_NOR_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_NO_NOR_EU305
	text = {
		trigger = {
			NOR = {

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU306
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU306
					has_country_flag = focus_EU306_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU306_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU306_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU306
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU306
					has_country_flag = focus_EU306_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU306_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU306
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU306
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU306
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU306_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU306_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU306_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU306_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU306_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU306
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU306_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU306_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU306_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU306_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU306_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU306_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU306_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU306_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU306_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

			POR = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = POR.EU_AI_focus_EU306_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = less_than
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = POR.EU_AI_focus_EU306_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = greater_than
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_POR_loc_key
	}
}
