#############
### EU307 ###
#############

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU307
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU307
					has_country_flag = focus_EU307_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU307_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU307_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU307
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU307
					has_country_flag = focus_EU307_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU307_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU307
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU307
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU307
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU307_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU307_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU307_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU307_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU307_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU307
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU307_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU307_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU307_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU307_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU307_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU307_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU307_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU307_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU307_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

### ALB EU307 ###
defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_ALB_EU307
	text = {
		trigger = {
			ALB = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU307_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_ALB_loc_key
	}
}

	name = EU_council_Undecided_ALB_EU307

				compare = less_than
			}

				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU307_voting_modifier_YES

				compare = greater_than

### EU308 ###
#############

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU308
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU308
					has_country_flag = focus_EU308_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU308_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU308_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU308
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU308
					has_country_flag = focus_EU308_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU308_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU308
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU308
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU308
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU308_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU308_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU308_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU308_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU308_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU308
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU308_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU308_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU308_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU308_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU308_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU308_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU308_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU308_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU308_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

### Voting TAGs loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU308
	text = {
		trigger = {
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					OR = {
						has_country_flag = focus_EU308_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU308_QMV_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU308_maj_yes
					}
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU308_loc_key
	}
}

### TAGs EU308 ###


### ALB EU308 ###
defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_ALB_EU308
	text = {
		trigger = {
			ALB = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}

### EU400 ###

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU400
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU400
					has_country_flag = focus_EU400_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU400_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU400_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU400
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU400
					has_country_flag = focus_EU400_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU400_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU400
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU400
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU400
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU400_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU400_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU400_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU400_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU400_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU400
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU400_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU400_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU400_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU400_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU400_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU400_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU400_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU400_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU400_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

	}

	name = EU_council_Undecided_SPR_EU400

		trigger = {
			SPR = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = SPR.EU_AI_focus_EU400_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = less_than
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = SPR.EU_AI_focus_EU400_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = greater_than
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_SPR_loc_key
	}

### EU401 ###

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU401
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU401
					has_country_flag = focus_EU401_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU401_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU401_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU401
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU401
					has_country_flag = focus_EU401_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU401_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU401
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU401
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU401
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU401_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU401_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU401_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU401_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU401_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU401
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU401_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU401_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU401_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU401_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU401_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU401_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU401_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU401_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU401_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_MLV_EU401
	text = {
		trigger = {
			MLV = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = MLV.EU_AI_focus_EU401_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_MLV_loc_key
	}
}

				var = SWI.EU_AI_focus_EU401_voting_modifier_YES

	}

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU402
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU402
					has_country_flag = focus_EU402_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU402_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU402_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU402
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU402
					has_country_flag = focus_EU402_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU402_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU402
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU402
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU402
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU402_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU402_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU402_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU402_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU402_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU402
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU402_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU402_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU402_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU402_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU402_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU402_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU402_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU402_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU402_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU403
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU403
					has_country_flag = focus_EU403_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU403_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU403_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU403
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU403
					has_country_flag = focus_EU403_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU403_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU403
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU403
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU403
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU403_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU403_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {

			}
			NOT = {

				}
			}
		}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU403
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU403_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU403_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU403_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU403_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU403_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU403_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU403_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU403_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU403_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

#############
### EU404 ###
#############

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU404
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU404
					has_country_flag = focus_EU404_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU404_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU404_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU404
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU404
					has_country_flag = focus_EU404_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU404_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU404
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU404
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU404
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU404_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU404_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU404_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU404_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU404_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU404
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU404_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU404_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU404_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU404_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU404_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU404_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU404_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU404_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU404_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

### Voting TAGs loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU404
	text = {
		trigger = {
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					OR = {
						has_country_flag = focus_EU404_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU404_QMV_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU404_maj_yes
					}
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU404_loc_key
	}

### ALB EU404 ###
defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_ALB_EU404
	text = {
		trigger = {
			ALB = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU404_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_ALB_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_Undecided_ALB_EU404
	text = {
		trigger = {
			ALB = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU404_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = less_than
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU404_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = greater_than
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_ALB_loc_key
	}

### EU405 ###

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU405
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU405
					has_country_flag = focus_EU405_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU405_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU405_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU405
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU405
					has_country_flag = focus_EU405_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU405_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU405
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU405
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU405
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU405_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU405_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU405_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU405_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU405_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU405
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU405_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU405_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU405_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU405_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU405_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU405_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU405_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU405_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU405_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

### Voting TAGs loc ###

	name = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU405
	text = {
		trigger = {
			NOT = {

					OR = {
						has_country_flag = focus_EU405_yes

						has_country_flag = focus_EU405_maj_yes
					}
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU405_loc_key
	}
}

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU406
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU406
					has_country_flag = focus_EU406_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU406_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU406_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU406
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU406
					has_country_flag = focus_EU406_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU406_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU406
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU406
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU406
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU406_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU406_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU406_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU406_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU406_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU406
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU406_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU406_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU406_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU406_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU406_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU406_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU406_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU406_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU406_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

			}

				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}

	}

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU407
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU407
					has_country_flag = focus_EU407_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU407_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU407_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU407
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU407
					has_country_flag = focus_EU407_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU407_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU407
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU407
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU407
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU407_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU407_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU407_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU407_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU407_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU407
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU407_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU407_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU407_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU407_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU407_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU407_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU407_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU407_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU407_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

		trigger = {
			FYR = {
				has_idea = EU_member

					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = FYR.EU_AI_focus_EU407_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = less_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_FYR_loc_key
	}
}

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU408
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU408
					has_country_flag = focus_EU408_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU408_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU408_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU408
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU408
					has_country_flag = focus_EU408_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU408_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU408
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU408
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU408
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU408_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU408_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU408_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU408_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU408_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU408
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU408_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU408_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU408_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU408_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU408_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU408_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU408_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU408_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU408_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

	name = EU_council_YES_GRE_EU408
	text = {
		trigger = {
			GRE = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = GRE.EU_AI_focus_EU408_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_GRE_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_Undecided_GRE_EU408
	text = {
		trigger = {
			GRE = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = GRE.EU_AI_focus_EU408_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = less_than
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = GRE.EU_AI_focus_EU408_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = greater_than
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_GRE_loc_key
	}
}

			}
			check_variable = {
				var = WAS.EU_AI_focus_EU408_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_WAS_loc_key
	}
}

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU500
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU500
					has_country_flag = focus_EU500_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU500_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU500_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU500
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU500
					has_country_flag = focus_EU500_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU500_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU500
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU500
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU500
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU500_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU500_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU500_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU500_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU500_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU500
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU500_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU500_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU500_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU500_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU500_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU500_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU500_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU500_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU500_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

#############
### EU600 ###
#############

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU600
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU600
					has_country_flag = focus_EU600_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU600_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU600_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU600
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU600
					has_country_flag = focus_EU600_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU600_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU600
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU600
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU600
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU600_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU600_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU600_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU600_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU600_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU600
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU600_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU600_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU600_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU600_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU600_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU600_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU600_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU600_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU600_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

### Voting TAGs loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU600
	text = {
		trigger = {
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					OR = {
						has_country_flag = focus_EU600_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU600_QMV_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU600_maj_yes
					}
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU600_loc_key
	}
}

### ALB EU600 ###
defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_ALB_EU600
	text = {
		trigger = {
			ALB = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU600_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_ALB_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_Undecided_ALB_EU600
	text = {
		trigger = {
			ALB = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU600_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = less_than
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU600_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = greater_than
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_ALB_loc_key
	}
}

### CZE EU600 ###
defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_CZE_EU600
	text = {
		trigger = {
			CZE = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = CZE.EU_AI_focus_EU600_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_CZE_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_Undecided_CZE_EU600
	text = {
		trigger = {
			CZE = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = CZE.EU_AI_focus_EU600_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = less_than
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = CZE.EU_AI_focus_EU600_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = greater_than
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_CZE_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_NO_CZE_EU600
	text = {
		trigger = {
			CZE = {
				has_idea = EU_member

				}

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU601
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU601
					has_country_flag = focus_EU601_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU601_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU601_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU601
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU601
					has_country_flag = focus_EU601_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU601_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU601
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU601
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU601
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU601_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU601_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU601_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU601_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU601_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU601
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU601_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU601_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU601_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU601_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU601_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU601_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU601_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU601_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU601_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

	text = {
		trigger = {
			ENG = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ENG.EU_AI_focus_EU601_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = less_than
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ENG.EU_AI_focus_EU601_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = greater_than
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_ENG_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_NO_ENG_EU601
	text = {
		trigger = {
			ENG = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ENG.EU_AI_focus_EU601_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = less_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_ENG_loc_key
	}
}

			}
			check_variable = {
				var = SLO.EU_AI_focus_EU601_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = greater_than
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_SLO_loc_key
	}
}

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU602
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU602
					has_country_flag = focus_EU602_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU602_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU602_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU602
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU602
					has_country_flag = focus_EU602_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU602_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU602
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU602
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU602
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU602_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU602_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU602_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU602_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU602_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU602
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU602_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU602_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU602_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU602_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU602_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU602_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU602_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU602_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU602_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

	text = {
		trigger = {
			AZE = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = AZE.EU_AI_focus_EU602_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_AZE_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_Undecided_AZE_EU602
	text = {
		trigger = {
			AZE = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = AZE.EU_AI_focus_EU602_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = less_than
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = AZE.EU_AI_focus_EU602_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = greater_than
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_AZE_loc_key
	}
}

			}
			check_variable = {
				var = SPR.EU_AI_focus_EU602_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = less_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_SPR_loc_key
	}
}

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU603
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU603
					has_country_flag = focus_EU603_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU603_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU603_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU603
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU603
					has_country_flag = focus_EU603_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU603_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU603
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU603
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU603
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU603_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU603_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU603_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU603_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU603_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU603
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU603_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU603_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU603_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU603_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU603_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU603_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU603_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU603_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU603_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = TUR.EU_AI_focus_EU603_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_TUR_loc_key
	}
}

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU700
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU700
					has_country_flag = focus_EU700_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU700_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU700_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU700
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU700
					has_country_flag = focus_EU700_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU700_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU700
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU700
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU700
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU700_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU700_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU700_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU700_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU700_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU700
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU700_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU700_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU700_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU700_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU700_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU700_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU700_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU700_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU700_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = WAS.EU_AI_focus_EU700_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = less_than
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = WAS.EU_AI_focus_EU700_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = greater_than
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_WAS_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_NO_WAS_EU700
	text = {
		trigger = {
			WAS = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU701
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU701
					has_country_flag = focus_EU701_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU701_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU701_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU701
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU701
					has_country_flag = focus_EU701_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU701_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU701
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU701
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU701
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU701_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU701_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU701_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU701_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU701_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU701
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU701_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU701_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU701_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU701_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU701_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU701_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU701_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU701_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU701_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_ALB_EU701
	text = {
		trigger = {
			ALB = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU701_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_ALB_loc_key
	}

#############
### EU702 ###
#############

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU702
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU702
					has_country_flag = focus_EU702_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU702_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU702_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU702
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU702
					has_country_flag = focus_EU702_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU702_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU702
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU702
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU702
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU702_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU702_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU702_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU702_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU702_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU702
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU702_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU702_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU702_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU702_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU702_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU702_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU702_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU702_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU702_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

### Voting TAGs loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU702
	text = {
		trigger = {
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					OR = {
						has_country_flag = focus_EU702_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU702_QMV_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU702_maj_yes
					}
				}
			}
		}

			ALB = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU702_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_ALB_loc_key
	}

			check_variable = {
				var = SCO.EU_AI_focus_EU702_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = less_than
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = SCO.EU_AI_focus_EU702_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = greater_than
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_SCO_loc_key
	}
}

### EU703 ###

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU703
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU703
					has_country_flag = focus_EU703_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU703_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU703_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU703
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU703
					has_country_flag = focus_EU703_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU703_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU703
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU703
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU703
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU703_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU703_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU703_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU703_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU703_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU703
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU703_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU703_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU703_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU703_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU703_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU703_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU703_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU703_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU703_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

			SLO = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = SLO.EU_AI_focus_EU703_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = less_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_SLO_loc_key
	}
}

### EU110 ###
#############

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU110
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU110
					has_country_flag = focus_EU110_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU110_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU110_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU110
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU110
					has_country_flag = focus_EU110_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU110_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU110
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU110
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU110
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU110_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU110_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU110_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU110_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU110_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU110
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU110_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU110_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU110_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU110_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU110_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU110_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU110_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU110_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU110_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

### Voting TAGs loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU110
	text = {
		trigger = {
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					OR = {
						has_country_flag = focus_EU110_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU110_QMV_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU110_maj_yes
					}
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU110_loc_key
	}
}

		trigger = {
			SWE = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = SWE.EU_AI_focus_EU110_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_SWE_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_Undecided_SWE_EU110

### EU111 ###

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU111
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU111
					has_country_flag = focus_EU111_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU111_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU111_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU111
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU111
					has_country_flag = focus_EU111_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU111_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU111
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU111
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU111
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU111_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU111_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU111_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU111_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU111_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU111
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU111_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU111_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU111_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU111_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU111_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU111_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU111_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU111_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU111_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

### Voting TAGs loc ###

	name = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU111
	text = {
		trigger = {
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					OR = {
						has_country_flag = focus_EU111_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU111_QMV_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU111_maj_yes
					}
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU111_loc_key
	}
}

	text = {
		trigger = {
			TUR = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = TUR.EU_AI_focus_EU111_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = less_than
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = TUR.EU_AI_focus_EU111_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = greater_than
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_TUR_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_NO_TUR_EU111
	text = {
		trigger = {
			TUR = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = TUR.EU_AI_focus_EU111_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = less_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_TUR_loc_key
	}
}

### EU112 ###
#############

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU112
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU112
					has_country_flag = focus_EU112_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU112_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU112_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU112
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU112
					has_country_flag = focus_EU112_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU112_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU112
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU112
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU112
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU112_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU112_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU112_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU112_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU112_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU112
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU112_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU112_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU112_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU112_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU112_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU112_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU112_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU112_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU112_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

### Voting TAGs loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU112
	text = {
		trigger = {
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					OR = {
						has_country_flag = focus_EU112_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU112_QMV_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU112_maj_yes
					}
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU112_loc_key
	}
}

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU113
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU113
					has_country_flag = focus_EU113_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU113_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU113_loc_key
	}
}

	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU113
	text = {

				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU113
					has_country_flag = focus_EU113_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU113_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU113
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU113
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU113
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU113_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU113_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {

				has_country_flag = focus_EU113_QMV
			}
			NOT = {

					has_country_flag = focus_EU113_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key

		}

}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU113
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU113_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU113_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU113_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU113_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU113_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU113_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU113_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU113_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU113_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

			}

				compare = greater_than_or_equals

		}

	}

					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ROM.EU_AI_focus_EU113_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = less_than
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ROM.EU_AI_focus_EU113_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = greater_than
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_ROM_loc_key
	}
}

#############
### EU604 ###
#############

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU604
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU604
					has_country_flag = focus_EU604_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU604_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU604_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU604
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU604
					has_country_flag = focus_EU604_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU604_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU604
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU604
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU604
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU604_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU604_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU604_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU604_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU604_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU604
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU604_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU604_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU604_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU604_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU604_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU604_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU604_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU604_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU604_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

### Voting TAGs loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU604
	text = {
		trigger = {
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					OR = {
						has_country_flag = focus_EU604_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU604_QMV_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU604_maj_yes
					}
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU604_loc_key
	}

### ALB EU604 ###
defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_ALB_EU604
	text = {
		trigger = {
			ALB = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU604_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_ALB_loc_key
	}
}

	name = EU_council_Undecided_ALB_EU604
