### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU605
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU605
					has_country_flag = focus_EU605_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU605_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU605_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU605
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU605
					has_country_flag = focus_EU605_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU605_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU605
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU605
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU605
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU605_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU605_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU605_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU605_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU605_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU605
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU605_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU605_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU605_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU605_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU605_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU605_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU605_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU605_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU605_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}

	}

### EU606 ###

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU606
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU606
					has_country_flag = focus_EU606_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU606_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU606_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU606
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU606
					has_country_flag = focus_EU606_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU606_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU606
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU606
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU606
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU606_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU606_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU606_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU606_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU606_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU606
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU606_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU606_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU606_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU606_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU606_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU606_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU606_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU606_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU606_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU607
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU607
					has_country_flag = focus_EU607_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU607_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU607_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU607
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU607
					has_country_flag = focus_EU607_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU607_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU607
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU607
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU607
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU607_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU607_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU607_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU607_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU607_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU607
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU607_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU607_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU607_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU607_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU607_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU607_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU607_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU607_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU607_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU608
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU608
					has_country_flag = focus_EU608_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU608_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU608_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU608
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU608
					has_country_flag = focus_EU608_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU608_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU608
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU608
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU608
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU608_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU608_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU608_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU608_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU608_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU608
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU608_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU608_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU608_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU608_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU608_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU608_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU608_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU608_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU608_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

				var = WAS.EU_AI_focus_EU608_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = less_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_WAS_loc_key
	}

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU609
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU609
					has_country_flag = focus_EU609_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU609_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU609_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU609
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU609
					has_country_flag = focus_EU609_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU609_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU609
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU609
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU609
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU609_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU609_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU609_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU609_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU609_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU609
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU609_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU609_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU609_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU609_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU609_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU609_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU609_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU609_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU609_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

### ALB EU609 ###
defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_ALB_EU609
	text = {
		trigger = {
			ALB = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU609_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_ALB_loc_key
	}
}

	name = EU_council_Undecided_ALB_EU609
	text = {
		trigger = {
			ALB = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU609_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = less_than
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU609_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = greater_than
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_ALB_loc_key
	}

	name = EU_council_YES_ICE_EU609
	text = {
		trigger = {
			ICE = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ICE.EU_AI_focus_EU609_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_ICE_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_Undecided_ICE_EU609
	text = {
		trigger = {
			ICE = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ICE.EU_AI_focus_EU609_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = less_than
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ICE.EU_AI_focus_EU609_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = greater_than
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_ICE_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_NO_ICE_EU609
	text = {

#############
### EU610 ###
#############

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU610
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU610
					has_country_flag = focus_EU610_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU610_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU610_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU610
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU610
					has_country_flag = focus_EU610_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU610_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU610
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU610
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU610
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU610_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU610_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU610_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU610_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU610_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU610
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU610_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU610_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU610_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU610_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU610_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU610_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU610_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU610_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU610_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}

### Voting TAGs loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU610
	text = {
		trigger = {
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					OR = {
						has_country_flag = focus_EU610_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU610_QMV_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU610_maj_yes
					}
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_YES_TAG_EU610_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_Undecided_TAG_EU610
	text = {
		trigger = {
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					OR = {
						has_country_flag = focus_EU610_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU610_QMV_yes
						has_country_flag = focus_EU610_maj_yes
					}
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_Undecided_TAG_EU610_loc_key
	}

### TAGs EU610 ###


### ALB EU610 ###
defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_YES_ALB_EU610
	text = {
		trigger = {
			ALB = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU610_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = greater_than_or_equals
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_ALB_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_Undecided_ALB_EU610
	text = {
		trigger = {
			ALB = {
				has_idea = EU_member
				NOT = {
					has_idea = EUU_voting_rights_suspended
				}
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU610_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 65
				compare = less_than
			}
			check_variable = {
				var = ALB.EU_AI_focus_EU610_voting_modifier_YES
				value = 35
				compare = greater_than
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_ALB_loc_key
	}
}

### focus loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_EU611
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU611
					has_country_flag = focus_EU611_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU611_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_focus_EU611_loc_key
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_focus_name_EU611
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member
				OR = {
					has_country_flag = focus_EU611
					has_country_flag = focus_EU611_QMV
					has_country_flag = focus_EU611_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU611
	}
}


### majority typ loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_majority_type_EU611
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU611
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU611_QMV
				}
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU611_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_unanimity_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU611_QMV
			}
			NOT = {			
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_country_flag = focus_EU611_maj
				}
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_QMV_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_country_flag = focus_EU611_maj
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_majority_loc_key
	}
}

### status loc ###

defined_text = {
	name = EU_council_status_EU611
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU611_accepted = yes
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_accepted_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
				has_global_flag = focus_EU611_retry
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_dismissed_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU611_draft = yes
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU611_retry
				}			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU611_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				focus_EU611_EP_approval = yes
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_draft_loc_key
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			focus_EU611_EP_approval = yes
			NOT = {
				focus_EU611_accepted = yes			
			}
			NOT = {
				any_of_scopes = {
				array = global.EU_member 
					has_global_flag = focus_EU611_retry
				}			
			}
		}
		localization_key = EU_council_EP_approval_loc_key
	}
}
